<subSubSection pageId="18" pageNumber="499" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="18.[132,775,1895,2027]" pageId="18" pageNumber="499">
REMARK. — Recent molecular evidence has led to the review of the family 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Lydekker" authorityYear="1891" box="[235,388,1922,1946]" class="Mammalia" family="Hipposideridae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="18" pageNumber="499" phylum="Chordata" rank="family">Hipposideridae</taxonomicName>
, with species traditionally placed within the genus 
<taxonomicName authority="Gray, 1831" authorityName="Gray" authorityYear="1831" box="[232,467,1949,1973]" class="Mammalia" family="Hipposideridae" genus="Hipposideros" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="18" pageNumber="499" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[232,351,1949,1973]" italics="true" pageId="18" pageNumber="499">Hipposideros</emphasis>
Gray, 1831
</taxonomicName>
assigned to three different genera, namely 
<taxonomicName authority="Peters, 1871" authorityName="Peters" authorityYear="1871" box="[251,480,1976,2000]" class="Mammalia" family="Mammalia (awaiting allocation)" genus="Doryrhina" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Mammalia (awaiting allocation)" pageId="18" pageNumber="499" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[251,350,1976,2000]" italics="true" pageId="18" pageNumber="499">Doryrhina</emphasis>
Peters, 1871
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName authority="Gray, 1831" authorityName="Gray" authorityYear="1831" box="[490,726,1976,2000]" class="Mammalia" family="Hipposideridae" genus="Hipposideros" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="18" pageNumber="499" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[490,609,1976,2000]" italics="true" pageId="18" pageNumber="499">Hipposideros</emphasis>
Gray, 1831
</taxonomicName>
, and 
<taxonomicName authority="Gray, 1866" authorityName="Gray" authorityYear="1866" box="[132,377,2003,2027]" class="Mammalia" family="Mammalia (awaiting allocation)" genus="Macronycteris" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Mammalia (awaiting allocation)" pageId="18" pageNumber="499" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[132,261,2004,2027]" italics="true" pageId="18" pageNumber="499">Macronycteris</emphasis>
Gray, 1866
</taxonomicName>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Foley" box="[392,554,2003,2027]" etAl="et al." firstAuthor="Foley" pageId="18" pageNumber="499" pagination="1 - 18" refId="ref25607" refString="FOLEY N. M., GOODMAN S. M., WHELAN C. V., PUECHMAILLE S. J. &amp; TEELING E. 2017. - Towards Navigating the Minotaur's Labyrinth: Cryptic Diversity and Taxonomic Revision within the speciose genus Hipposideros (Hipposideridae), Acta Chiropterologica 19: 1 - 18. https: // doi. org / 10.3161 / 15081109 ACC 2017.19.1.001" type="journal article" year="2017">
